.TH "CLIFM" "1" "Jul 18, 2023" "clifm 1.13.1" "CLIFM Manual"
.SH NAME
clifm \- The Command Line File Manager
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B clifm
[\fI\,OPTION\/\fR]... [\fI\,PATH\/\fR]

.SH INDEX
